<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HackUMass XIII Check-In Instructions</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1625 0%, #2d1b3d 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #7c3aed;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #f8f4ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #7c3aed;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        .info-box strong {
            color: #7c3aed;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .qr-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .qr-container img {
            max-width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            border: 3px solid #7c3aed;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
        }

        .qr-label {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #7c3aed;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .warning {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        ol,
        ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéâ Welcome to the HackUMass XIII!</h1>
            <p>Check-In Instructions for <%= teamName %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2>üìã Important: Two-Step Check-In Process</h2>
                <p>To participate in HackUMass XIII, you must complete BOTH check-in steps. Please read carefully:</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>üìç Check-In Location:</strong>
                Organizer Desk in front of the Organizer Room, ILC
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>‚è∞ Check-In Time Window:</strong>
                Sunday, February 9th, 2025<br>
                10:00 AM - 11:30 AM
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Step 1: Organizer Desk Check-In</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Come to the <strong>Organizer Desk in front of the Organizer Room in the ILC</strong></li>
                    <li>Show the QR code below to our scanner</li>
                    <li>You will be assigned your table and room number</li>
                    <li>You'll receive a confirmation email with your assignment</li>
                </ol>

                <div class="qr-container">
                    <img src="cid:checkinQR" alt="Check-In QR Code">
                    <div class="qr-label">Show this QR code at the Organizer Desk</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Step 2: Table QR Code Scan</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>After completing Step 1, go to your assigned table</li>
                    <li>Click the button below to access the check-in page</li>
                    <li>Scan the QR code present at your table using the page</li>
                    <li>This confirms your presence at your assigned location</li>
                </ol>

                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="<%= checkin2Link %>" class="button">Complete Step 2 Check-In</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> You MUST complete BOTH check-in steps. Step 2 can only be completed AFTER
                you've checked in at the Organizer Desk and received your table assignment.
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2>Need Help?</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or encounter issues during check-in, please approach the organizers at the
                    desk. We're here to help!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Good luck with your hackathon project!</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 12px;">This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>